<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your {{questionnaire.title}} Results</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .score-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .score {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .risk-level {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .risk-low {
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #047857;
    }
    .risk-medium {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      color: #92400e;
    }
    .risk-high {
      background-color: #fee2e2;
      color: #b91c1c;
    }
    .unique-code {
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Your {{questionnaire.title}} Results</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for completing the {{questionnaire.title}} questionnaire.</p>
      
      <p>Your unique response code is:</p>
      <div class="unique-code">{{uniqueCode}}</div>
      <p>Please save this code for future reference. You can use it to access your results at any time.</p>
      
      <div class="score-container">
        <p>Your score:</p>
        <div class="score">{{score}}</div>
        
        {{#if riskLevel}}
          <div class="risk-level risk-{{riskLevel}}">
            {{riskLevel}} RISK
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      
      {{#if viewResultsUrl}}
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{viewResultsUrl}}" class="button">View Detailed Results</a>
        </p>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p>If you have any questions about your results, please contact your healthcare provider.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This email was sent from MindTrack, a mental health tracking application.</p>
      <p>Date: {{date}}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
